    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedboat Simulator 是一款真实的快艇竞速游戏，你可以驾驶高速快艇，定制它们的颜色，并参加激动人心的比赛。在夏威夷水域中航行，冲过终点线时尽情展示你的风采！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/6bbd81ee85a7af707001a9cc7215785c.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Speedboat Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedboat Simulator 是一款刺激的快艇竞速体验，将真实的模拟与高速动作结合在一起。驾驶强力的快艇，每艘快艇都有独特的操控性和加速能力，在各种具有挑战性的赛道上测试你的技巧。定制你的快艇颜色，并与对手在激烈的比赛中一较高下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/7e39c036de1e5d7e12fdc56f2cee88fb.webp?t=1772360610\" width=593 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.poster.avif?t=1772360610\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.webm?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258500/extras/43c247f2adb012b0d9d87592b152e01a.mp4?t=1772360610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含多个游戏模式，包括单人模式和观众模式，允许玩家竞速或观看比赛的精彩过程。凭借灵敏的控制、动态水面物理效果和令人肾上腺素飙升的速度，每场比赛都是与时间和对手的对决。随着游戏的发展，玩家将体验更多的快艇、赛道和定制选项，提供无限的方式来享受终极的快艇竞速体验！</p>",
